{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "pos-backend-complete-2026",
		"name": "POS Backend - Complete API Collection",
		"description": "# POS Backend API - Complete Documentation\n\nComprehensive API collection for the Point of Sale Backend system.\n\n## 🔐 Authentication\n\nAll endpoints (except login/register) require:\n- **Bearer Token**: Sanctum authentication token\n- **X-Business-Id Header**: Current business context ID (for most endpoints)\n- **X-Device-Id Header**: Device identifier (for sync endpoints)\n\n## 📋 Features\n\n- **Multi-tenant** - Business isolation with branch management\n- **Role-based permissions** - Granular access control\n- **PIN Authentication** - Quick login with 4-6 digit PIN\n- **Inventory Management** - Stock tracking, batches, expiry dates (FEFO)\n- **Shelf-Store Inventory** - Separate shelf and store stock management\n- **Sales Management** - POS transactions, shifts, payments\n- **Financial Analytics** - Revenue, profit, growth trends\n- **Approval Workflows** - Quick sales, refunds, stock transfers\n- **Stock Write-offs** - Track damaged/expired inventory\n- **Offline Sync** - Device registration and data synchronization\n\n## 🚀 Quick Start\n\n1. Login to get authentication token\n2. Set `auth_token` and `business_id` variables\n3. Start making authenticated requests\n\n## 📊 Modules\n\n- Authentication & User Management (with PIN support)\n- Business & Branch Management\n- Product & Inventory Management\n- Branch-Product Management (Shelf/Store)\n- Sales & Payments\n- Sales Shifts\n- Quick Sales, Refunds & Stock Transfers\n- Stock Write-offs\n- Analytics & Reporting\n- Batch & Expiry Management\n- Offline Sync & Device Management\n\nVersion: 2.0.0\nLast Updated: February 8, 2026",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"auth": {
		"type": "bearer",
		"bearer": [
			{
				"key": "token",
				"value": "{{auth_token}}",
				"type": "string"
			}
		]
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Authentication",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Register New User",
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "noauth"
						},
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json"
							},
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n    \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n    \"password\": \"password123\",\n    \"password_confirmation\": \"password123\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/register",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "register"]
						},
						"description": "Register a new user account.\n\n**No authentication required**"
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Login",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"auth_token\", jsonData.token);",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"user_id\", jsonData.user.id);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "noauth"
						},
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n    \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
							"options": {
								"raw": {
									"language": "json"
								}
							}
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/login",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "login"]
						},
						"description": "Authenticate user and receive Sanctum token.\n\n**Returns:**\n- Authentication token\n- User details\n- Current business context\n\n**Auto-saves token to collection variables**"
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "Login Success",
							"originalRequest": {
								"method": "POST",
								"header": [],
								"body": {
									"mode": "raw",
									"raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n    \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
									"options": {
										"raw": {
											"language": "json"
										}
									}
								},
								"url": {
									"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/login",
									"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
									"path": ["api", "login"]
								}
							},
							"status": "OK",
							"code": 200,
							"_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
							"header": [],
							"cookie": [],
							"body": "{\n    \"user\": {\n        \"id\": 1,\n        \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n        \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n        \"current_business_id\": 1\n    },\n    \"token\": \"1|abc123def456ghi789jkl012mno345pqr678stu901vwx234yz\"\n}"
						}
					]
				},
